Title: Spelling Bee Archive 2012
Author: চ্যাম্পস২১.কম
Summary:
"For the 1st time in 2012, Champs21.com organized the internationally acclaimed   TV reality show Spelling Bee in Bangladesh. All episodes aired are accumulated in this single pack. Participants who would compete in coming years can also prepare themselves for qualifying rounds of the competition, and specially for nerve wrecking TV round by watching the past episodes. Spelling Bee Archive 2012 is a collector’s edition.

This 5 DVD, 30 episode Spelling Bee Archive 2012 contains:

·         DVD 1: Episodes 1 – 6 [Preparatory episodes
